{"tid":130514,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[風水] 咁樣係咪屋企風水有問題","createTime":"2017-02-22T12:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T16:29:01.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26dfd4b559801ee35a8f0a3370ac02810857dcd3","tid":130514,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"件事發生係我親戚屋企到既<br />\n<br />\n話說佢有3個仔女，兩男一女<br />\n<br />\n咁我由細睇到佢地大，一直身體都算壯健同青靚白淨既。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來早幾年佢地搬左新屋 ，兩兄弟訓同一間房，個女就另外一間房<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知係巧合定點，自從搬左屋之後，個兩兄弟就開始爆暗瘡，一樣係腸胃同精神都變差左，反而其他人咩事都無。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底係咪間睡房出左事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f035198226949b959bc50cea03f21b96f71a46a8","tid":130514,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ac93052d9a5b3423bc71ef34c0e02dc51950fa","tid":130514,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"青春期，開始打丁，打丁上癮影響身體"},{"pid":"23dd976cd204dba9011b6fa6a9e1288cdd857b25","tid":130514,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青春期，開始打丁，打丁上癮影響身體</blockquote><br />\n都唔係廿歲先開始青春期掛"},{"pid":"5f9f9945fdaec7b88f9c95bf69eed70944720462","tid":130514,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b332f74ea8715d058f9b319ac72c1419547e2b","tid":130514,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c7fbbecffd2826f0240f1e89088cba9c53e9c789","tid":130514,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img sr